HEADWORD: Aristotelian
<hw>Ar`is*to*te"li*an</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to Aristotle, the famous Greek philosopher (384-322 <sc>b.
c</sc>.).</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A follower of Aristotle; a
Peripatetic. See <er>Peripatetic</er>.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

